Estuaries

August 2002 , Volume 25, Issue 4 , pp 704–726 | Cite as
Harmful algal blooms and eutrophication: Nutrient sources, composition, and consequences

    Authors
    Authors and affiliations

    Donald M. Anderson Email author
    Patricia M. Glibert
    Joann M. Burkholder

    Donald M. Anderson
        1
    Email author
    Patricia M. Glibert
        2
